# Reset Password Test Cases

## Overview
This document contains manual test cases for the Reset Password feature of https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/web/index.php/auth/login
The purpose of these test cases is to ensure the Reset Password functionality works correctly.

---

## Test Data
- Valid Username: Admin 
- Invalid Username: 123admin

---

## Test Cases

| Test Case ID | Test Scenario (Positive/Negative Case) | Preconditions | Test Steps | Expected Result |
|-------------|---------------|------------|----------------|----------|--------|
| TC-RP-01 | Success Reset Password (Positive Case) | Success access login page | 1. Click "Forgot your password?" text, it will navigate to Reset Password page<br>2. input valid username<br>3. Click Reset Password| It will be navigated to "Reset Password link sent successfully" page and password link is sent to valid email|
| TC-RP-02 | Failed Reset Password, input invalid username (Negative Case) | Success access login page | 1. Click "Forgot your password?" text, it will navigate to Reset Password page<br>2. input invalid username<br>3. Click Reset Password| It will be navigated to "Username is invalid" page |
| TC-RP-03 | Failed Reset Password, click Reset Password button without input valid usermame (Negative Case) | Success access login page | 1. Click "Forgot your password?" text, it will navigate to Reset Password page<br>2. Click Reset Password without input username| There will be an error to input username |

